==English==
=== Noun ===
'''natural number'''

# {{mathematics}} Any [[non-negative]] [[integer]]; any [[member]] of the [[set]] of [[natural numbers]].
# {{mathematics}} A [[counting number]] or [[whole number]]; a [[positive]] [[integer]].
====Usage notes====
'''Please note:''' This term is ambiguous so that careful authors will define it. Common guidelines are:
* ''non-negative integers'' are used in [[set theory]] and [[computer science]].
* ''positive integers'' are used in [[number theory]] 
====Synonyms====
(''positive integer''): [[counting number]], [[whole number]].
